columns.dc:description: In a Form 4 or Form 5, true for a reporting person not subject to Section 16 and no transaction or holdings reporting in <nonDerativeTable> and <DerativeTable> sections of document

columns.name: FORM3_HOLDINGS_REPORTED
columns.dc:description: EDGAR derived value on Form 3 or Form 4 based on the number of <nonDerivativeHolding> and <derivativeHolding> elements with a <transactionFormType> value of “3.” If at least one “3” holding is being reported, EDGAR will set this element to true. Otherwise, it will be set to false

columns.name: FORM4_TRANS_REPORTED
columns.dc:description: EDGAR derived value on Form 3 or Form 4 based on the number of <nonDerivativeTransaction> and <derivativeTransaction> elements with a <transactionFormType> value of “4.” If at least one “4” transaction is being reported, EDGAR will set this element to true. Otherwise, it will be set to false
